---
title: Double Middle Eastern Beef Koftas & Pea Pod Salad with Lemon Yoghurt
description: These juicy Middle Eastern-spiced beef koftas are calling your name - don’t keep them waiting! Packed with warm, aromatic flavours, these protein parcels pair perfectly with a crisp pea pod salad for a refreshing crunch. Dollop over a zesty lemon yoghurt, and you’ve got a meal that’s vibrant, hearty, and downright irresistible!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
